recent_25_results.question: 1.7 What is the main difference between a while and a do...while statement?
recent_25_results.student_answer: 1.7 "The "do" statement first evaluates the condition and then executes the lines of code in the statement 0 or more times. The "do while" statement executes the lines of code and then it evaluates the condition. "
